  <h2>How to add a player</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Click the <strong>Add Player</strong> button to open the player form.</li>
    <li>Fill in required fields: first name, last name, date of birth (if applicable), playing position, and contact details.</li>
    <li>Provide emergency contact details and any important medical notes.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Save</strong> to add the player to your club roster.</li>
  </ol>

